Create a shard using XJSON format with id, port, runtime, api, and optionally view. Example:
```js
const shard = {
  id: 'users',
  port: 3001,
  runtime: 'kuhul',
  api: [{path: '/list', method: 'GET'}]
};
await klh.registerShard(shard);
```
